      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="droplet" size={22} /></div>
        <h4>Oxygen Utilization</h4>
        <p>Clinical trials show cordyceps improves VO2max — the maximum rate of oxygen consumption during exercise. Better oxygen utilization means more aerobic capacity at every intensity level, from walking to sprinting.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="fitness" size={22} /></div>
