        <p>A 2016 study found Cordyceps militaris improved time to exhaustion and delayed the onset of fatigue during high-intensity exercise in healthy adults. The effect is cumulative — benefits increase with consistent daily supplementation over 4-12 weeks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="shield" size={22} /></div>
        <h4>Anti-Fatigue Effect</h4>
        <p>Cordyceps reduces blood lactate accumulation during exercise, delaying the burning sensation and fatigue that limits high-intensity performance. It also supports faster post-exercise lactate clearance for improved recovery between sets or intervals.</p>
      </div>
